Package fr.epita.iam.views

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Create
    Description This JPanel class is used to create the identities and persist them in the database.
    Login
    Description This JPanel class is used to validate Users or direct to a JPanel class to create a User and persist in the database.
    MainFrame
    Description This class allows to manage the different views of the GUI, it's also responsible for resizing the windows as they change from window to window.
    PopUp
    Description This class is used to generate customized PopUps messages as needed.
    SearchDeleteUpdate
    Description This JPanel class is used to manage the identities persisted in the database (more concretely: Search, Delete and Update operations).
    SignUp
    Description This JPanel class is used to create Users with an identity and persist it in the database.
